Package org.jfree.chart.renderer

Class HighLow

java.lang.Object
org.jfree.chart.renderer.HighLow
public class HighLow
extends Object
Represents one point in the high/low/open/close plot.

All the coordinates in this class are in Java2D space.

Author:
Andrzej Porebski
